            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true" class="mb-4"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
            <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-semibold mb-2" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Emergency Contacts, Rally Points, and Check-Ins for Every Trip Leader</h3>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">During your trip, every team leader gets the SafeTrekr mobile app -- live geofencing, muster check-ins, rally point navigation, SMS broadcast, and morning/evening safety briefings. For tournament travel: coach and chaperone check-in protocols that document SafeSport compliance in real time.</p>
